sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Spring TaskScheduler
    participant SRV as CoursClassroomServiceImpl
    participant DB as MySQL Database

    loop Every 60 seconds (fixedRate = 60000)
        S->>SRV: Trigger @Scheduled method
        SRV->>SRV: execute task (e.g. archiving)
        SRV->>DB: Update entities status
        DB-->>SRV: Confirmation
        SRV-->>S: Task Completed
    end
